{"tid":2050020,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"蔡英文：在地球上其他地方 每一分鐘就有60秒過去","createTime":"2020-06-04T00:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T01:35:40.000Z","uid":2054,"like":102,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8d1aab3387f2c636a1d9317cc72d0376d21a27","tid":2050020,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:50:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10156779055016065/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F46251501064%2Fposts%2F10156779055016065%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Fi4Me5dMHeyo7M%2BwlVraY%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=f424a680\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10156779055016065/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n在地球上其他地方，每一分鐘就有60秒過去。<br />\n　　 <br />\n可是在中國，每一年卻只有364個日子，有一天被遺忘掉了。<br />\n　　<br />\n過去在台灣，我們也曾經有許多日子，不能出現在日曆上面，但我們一個一個把它們找回來了。因為我們不必再隱匿歷史，所以我們可以共同思索未來。<br />\n　　<br />\n希望這世界上每一個角落、每一片土地，都不要再有消失的日子。也祝福香港。<br />\n　　<br />\n#自由的台灣撐香港的自由"},{"pid":"f32c52f18978fbc5db578a5e3e5aa2712cbc5d1f","tid":2050020,"uid":289946,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19b5b7dadb9eb27d66e2487b2943f0916c3add67","tid":2050020,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63550849c9794c12538e781fb802ee9ff21a85d0","tid":2050020,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"ccd8d3fce0d011c5350c81a2c24eb16dbc3c9f81","tid":2050020,"uid":1579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T00:56:23.000Z","msg":"好感動<img src=\"/assets/